OL,3,CInquest opens into death of 11-year-
OL,4,Cold last seen entering river
OL,6,FA final inquest into the death of an
OL,7,F11-year-old who died after getting
OL,8,Finto difficulty in the River Don will
OL,9,Ftake place in February next year.
OL,11,FMackenzie Swift was last seen entering
OL,12,Fthe river near Mexborough in South
OL,13,FYorkshire on Saturday May 30.
OL,15,FHe did not emerge from the water and a
OL,16,F48-hour search recovered his body on
OL,17,FJune 2.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
