OL,3,CInquest opens into death of 11-year-
OL,4,Cold last seen entering river
OL,6,FIn a hearing at Doncaster Coroner's
OL,7,FCourt on Thursday June 11, the court
OL,8,Fheard emergency services were alerted
OL,9,Fto a report of a child in difficulty
OL,10,Fin the water.
OL,12,FCoroner's officer Siobhan Golightly
OL,13,Fsaid: "Upon arrival the emergency
OL,14,Fservices launched an extensive search
OL,15,Fand rescue operation.
OL,17,F"Although the precise cause of death
OL,18,Fis yet to be confirmed, the
OL,19,Fpathologist noted features in keeping
OL,20,Fwith drowning."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781183478
OL,3,CInquest opens into death of 11-year-
OL,4,Cold last seen entering river
OL,6,FThe hearing was told Mackenzie's body
OL,7,Fcould be released to his family for
OL,8,Fthe funeral, and a final inquest into
OL,9,Fhis death would take place on February
OL,10,F16 next year.
OL,12,FArea coroner Louise Slater said: "I
OL,13,Fwould like to wish my most heartfelt
OL,14,Fcondolences to Mackenzie's family at
OL,15,Fthis most difficult time."
OL,17,FA fundraising page for Mackenzie has
OL,18,Falmost hit its #18,000 target.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
