OL,3,CInquest opens into death of 11-year-
OL,4,Cold last seen entering river
OL,6,FMackenzie's death comes after a period
OL,7,Fof other open water related deaths
OL,8,Facross the country after a spell of
OL,9,Frecent hot weather. 17 died nationally
OL,10,Fincluding many from the Calendar
OL,11,Fregion.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
